&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen with the Garstang District Nursing Team for a full time Band 5 Staff Nurse. This is a permanent position.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Garstang District Nurses are a supportive team who are innovative, enthusiastic, enjoy developing staff and have a positive attitude to change, if you share these qualities we would like to hear from you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please ensure you have read the personal specifications/ job description and you are able to demonstrate you meet this criteria in your supporting evidence.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you would like to meet with myself and some of the team prior to applying, you would be more than welcome to attend.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NMC Level 1 Registration (Adult Branch), IT skills and car driver essential, enhanced CBS clearance required.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
